reviewText:
Absolutely, without a doubt at all, the biggest waste of celluloid in history.  First of all, you think of a "movie"
being of some substantial length, thus one doesn't usually check to see if a movie being sold is only a 15 minute,
low budget, totally pointless dvd.  However, in retrospect, I did find use for the dvd case after I trashed the contents.  DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY!!!
